				Posted in <a href="http://joythebaker.com/category/recipes/" rel="category tag">Recipes</a>, <a href="http://joythebaker.com/category/snacks/" rel="category tag">Snacks</a>			</span>
			
						<span class="tags-links">
				- Tagged <a href="http://joythebaker.com/tag/cat-treats/" rel="tag">cat treats</a>			</span>
					
