<article id="post-17499" class="post-17499 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-bread category-breakfast category-chocolate category-recipes tag-breakfast tag-brunch tag-cinnamon-rolls tag-easy tag-espresso tag-fast tag-recipe tag-yeast">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://joythebaker.com/2015/01/quick-dirty-chocolate-espresso-cinnamon-rolls/" rel="bookmark">Quick and Dirty Chocolate Espresso Cinnamon Rolls</a></h1>		
				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://joythebaker.com/2015/01/quick-dirty-chocolate-espresso-cinnamon-rolls/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-01-26T08:23:14+00:00">January 26, 2015</time></a></span><span class="byline"> - <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://joythebaker.com/author/joythebaker/">joythebaker</a></span></span>						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://joythebaker.com/2015/01/quick-dirty-chocolate-espresso-cinnamon-rolls/#comments" title="Comment on Quick and Dirty Chocolate Espresso Cinnamon Rolls">83 Comments</a></span>
					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
				<div class="entry-thumbnail">
			<img width="640" height="960" src="http://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Quick-and-Dirty-Chocolate-Espresso-Cinnamon-Rolls-6-e1422251647541.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Quick and Dirty Chocolate Espresso Cinnamon Rolls" />		</div>
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>
		<span class="pibfi_pinterest ">
		<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-17503" src="http://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Quick-and-Dirty-Chocolate-Espresso-Cinnamon-Rolls-6-e1422251647541.jpg" alt="Quick and Dirty Chocolate Espresso Cinnamon Rolls" width="640" height="960"/>
			<span class="xc_pin" onclick="pin_this(event, 'http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://joythebaker.com/2015/01/quick-dirty-chocolate-espresso-cinnamon-rolls/&amp;media=http://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Quick-and-Dirty-Chocolate-Espresso-Cinnamon-Rolls-6-e1422251647541.jpg&amp;description=Quick and Dirty Chocolate Espresso Cinnamon Rolls | http://joythebaker.com/2015/01/quick-dirty-chocolate-espresso-cinnamon-rolls/')">
			</span>
		</span>
	</p>
<span class="dropcap">H</span>ow can I do the least amount of work, but still get the most amount of cinnamon rolls into my mouth? &nbsp;Super valid question.</p>
<p>How long would it take&nbsp;to go through airport security and stand in line at the Terminal C Cinnamon? &nbsp;Is that time shorter than the time it would take to make yeasted dough, roll it, fill it, slice it, rise it, and bake it? &nbsp;</p>
<p>How can I go from zero to cinnamon roll in one hour flat? &nbsp;</p>
<p>Here&#8217;s how! &nbsp;Ready. &nbsp;Set. &nbsp;You know&#8230;.&nbsp;</p>
<p> <a href="http://joythebaker.com/2015/01/quick-dirty-chocolate-espresso-cinnamon-rolls/#more-17499" class="more-link">Read more</a></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
	<footer class="entry-footer">
